WEBVTT

00:11.272 --> 00:12.969
Previously onGood Sam...

00:13.013 --> 00:15.189
GRIFF: You're supervising
these doctors.

00:15.232 --> 00:18.148
You're above them in
knowledge, rank and skill.

00:18.192 --> 00:19.715
Act like it.

00:19.758 --> 00:21.934
SAM:
It's like undermining me
as a sport for him.

00:21.978 --> 00:23.893
I think I'm gonna take
the Cleveland offer, Caleb.

00:23.936 --> 00:24.937
You don't want to do that.

00:24.981 --> 00:27.766
Are you saying I should stay?

00:27.810 --> 00:30.552
It's not about me.Yeah.

00:30.595 --> 00:33.859
[gunshot][screaming]

00:33.903 --> 00:35.078
Dad!

00:37.733 --> 00:42.172
My father can never be replaced,
but I vow to carry on his legacy

00:42.216 --> 00:43.565
to the best of my ability.

00:43.608 --> 00:45.045
You've earned this.

00:45.088 --> 00:47.134
And I say that
as your chief medical officer,

00:47.177 --> 00:49.658
not your mother.

00:49.788 --> 00:51.486
I'm Sam, by the way.I'm Malcolm.

00:51.529 --> 00:53.662
Kingsley. I'm the new director of finance.

00:53.705 --> 00:55.446
VIVIAN:
Sam!
Mom?

00:55.490 --> 00:56.534
It's your father.

00:56.578 --> 00:58.406
He's waking up.

00:58.449 --> 01:00.364
You were shot six months ago.

01:00.408 --> 01:02.236
How long...

01:02.279 --> 01:04.194
till I can work again?

01:04.238 --> 01:05.935
You have to be proctored.

01:05.978 --> 01:07.371
GRIFF:
Oh, come on.

01:07.415 --> 01:08.590
It's state law.

01:08.633 --> 01:11.941
I'll do it.
I'll supervise him.

01:12.724 --> 01:14.204
What, do you have company?

01:14.248 --> 01:15.945
I wanted to tell you.

01:15.988 --> 01:19.427
VIVIAN:
A resident, Griff?
Sam's best friend.

01:19.470 --> 01:21.559
I've decided to continue
proctoring you,

01:21.603 --> 01:22.691
if that's what you want.

01:22.734 --> 01:24.171
I want to be very clear.

01:24.214 --> 01:27.870
I am making this decision
as a doctor.

01:27.913 --> 01:30.525
As your daughter,
I'm calling it.

01:33.528 --> 01:36.096
♪

01:43.625 --> 01:46.062
[engine revs]

01:47.411 --> 01:48.891
[horn honking]

01:53.852 --> 01:55.071
Good morning, boss.

01:55.115 --> 01:56.942
Getting to work bright
and early.

01:56.986 --> 01:59.293
Bright and early means arriving
before the boss.

01:59.336 --> 02:00.642
Who says I won't?

02:00.685 --> 02:02.644
[engine revving]

